Overview

Istockhomes is a modular asset listing platform supporting multiple verticals:

Real Estate

Yacht / Marine

Aircraft

Luxury Rentals

Art

Business

Future: Dating

The system allows developers to build independent mobile apps (iOS, Android, Web) that connect to the central Istockhomes database using a controlled public API.

