ğŸ§  AI Listing Flow

File:

/App/index.php


Flow:

User uploads image

Geolocation captured (browser)

OpenCage resolves address

OpenAI analyzes image

JSON returned:

title

category

price

description

Redirect to:

edit-listing.php

