ğŸ”’ Privacy Rules

The following fields are never exposed:

email

phone

password_hash

tokens

verification codes

biometric credentials

PayPal accounts

Location Privacy
Yacht / Aircraft

Address removed

GPS rounded (2 decimals)

Dating (future table)

Address removed

GPS removed

Luxury Rentals

Address allowed

GPS rounded (3 decimals)

Homes For Sale

Full address allowed

Full GPS allowed

listings.show_location = 0

GPS always removed

