Core asset table supporting:

Real Estate

Marine

Aircraft

Vehicles

Art

Business

Includes:

title

price

category

description

latitude / longitude

address

aircraft_* fields

marine_* fields

charter_available

sold

franchise_branding

Controls white-label appearance:

franchise_id

logo_path

header_bg_color

accent_color

contact_name

contact_email

contact_phone

ğŸ— Developer Philosophy

Developers may:

Build their own frontend apps

Choose fields they need

Respect vertical privacy rules

Use their own Apple / Google accounts

Host independently

All public access is through:

/App/dev.php


No direct DB access allowed.

ğŸ§­ Example Use Cases
iOS Yacht Charter App

Query listings where category = Marine

Use vertical=yacht

Build map using rounded GPS

Real Estate App

Query listings where category = Real Estate

Use vertical=homes_for_sale

Show address + full location

Aircraft Marketplace

Query category = Aircraft

Use vertical=aircraft

Hide exact airport location

